default.text:
'XCM Chains'

In Referendum 222 the community voted on whether to extend the lease of Statemine by about two more years (16 lease periods). With the upcoming rollout of XCMv3 and additional features like locking over XCM, Statemine will take on more 'system level' functionalities.
